**Automatic protection activation on import** - Just add one line to protect your Python applications!

```python
import kil0p3  # ğŸ›¡ï¸ Protection starts automatically!
```

## âœ¨ Features

- ğŸ”‘ **License validation** with digital signatures
- ğŸ–¥ï¸ **Hardware ID (HWID) binding** 
